data.title: HELP ME identify this music video?

It was a catchy tune
All the band are dressed as skeletons

data.text:
My dad has been going on about this music video for years:

It was a catchy tune

All the band are dressed as skeletons

They were all dancing in rhythm

This controversy has been going on for about 15-20 years in my house! Please help! None of us can identify it.

We have already guessed

Bones - The Killers

Hey Boy Hey Girl - Chemical Brothers

Around the World - Daft Punk

He says it isn't any of these... any ideas?!?! It would be the best Christmas present ever.
